http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent.label: Agent
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent.definition: An agent (eg. person, group, software or physical artifact).

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Project.label: Project
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Project.definition: A project (a collective endeavour of some kind).

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/LabelProperty.label: Label Property
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/LabelProperty.definition: A foaf:LabelProperty is any RDF property with texual values that serve as labels.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/account.label: account
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/account.definition: Indicates an account held by this agent.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/accountName.label: account name
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/accountName.definition: Indicates the name (identifier) associated with this online account.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/accountService.label: account service homepage
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/accountService.definition: Indicates a homepage of the service provide for this online account.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/age.label: age
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/age.definition: The age in years of some agent.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/nick.label: nickname
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/nick.definition: A short informal nickname characterising an agent (includes login identifiers, IRC and other chat nicknames).

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/based_near.label: based near
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/based_near.definition: A location that something is based near, for some broadly human notion of near.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/birthday.label: birthday
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/birthday.definition: The birthday of this Agent, represented in mm-dd string form, eg. '12-31'.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/currentProject.label: current project
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/currentProject.definition: A current project this person works on.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/depicts.label: depicts
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/depicts.definition: A thing depicted in this representation.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/dnaChecksum.label: DNA checksum
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/dnaChecksum.definition: A checksum for the DNA of some thing. Joke.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/familyName.label: familyName
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/familyName.definition: The family name of some person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/family_name.label: family_name
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/family_name.definition: The family name of some person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/firstName.label: firstName
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/firstName.definition: The first name of a person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/focus.label: focus
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/focus.definition: The underlying or 'focal' entity associated with some SKOS-described concept.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/fundedBy.label: funded by
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/fundedBy.definition: An organization funding a project or person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/geekcode.label: geekcode
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/geekcode.definition: A textual geekcode for this person, see http://www.geekcode.com/geek.html

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/gender.label: gender
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/gender.definition: The gender of this Agent (typically but not necessarily 'male' or 'female').

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/givenName.label: Given name
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/givenName.definition: The given name of some person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/givenname.label: Given name
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/givenname.definition: The given name of some person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/holdsAccount.label: account
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/holdsAccount.definition: Indicates an account held by this agent.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/isPrimaryTopic.label: is primary topic of
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/isPrimaryTopic.definition: A document that this thing is the primary topic of.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page.label: page
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page.definition: A page or document about this thing.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/img.label: image
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/img.definition: An image that can be used to represent some thing (ie. those depictions which are particularly representative of something, eg. one's photo on a homepage).

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/interest.label: interest
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/interest.definition: A page about a topic of interest to this person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/primaryTopic.label: primary topic
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/primaryTopic.definition: The primary topic of some page or document.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/knows.label: knows
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/knows.definition: A person known by this person (indicating some level of reciprocated interaction between the parties).

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/lastName.label: lastName
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/lastName.definition: The last name of a person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/made.label: made
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/made.definition: Something that was made by this agent.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/maker.label: maker
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/maker.definition: An agent that  made this thing.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/mbox.label: personal mailbox
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/mbox.definition: A  personal mailbox, ie. an Internet mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the first owner of this mailbox. This is a 'static inverse functional property', in that  there is (across time and change) at most one individual that ever has any particular value for foaf:mbox.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/mbox_sha1sum.label: sha1sum of a personal mailbox URI name
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/mbox_sha1sum.definition: The sha1sum of the URI of an Internet mailbox associated with exactly one owner, the  first owner of the mailbox.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/member.label: member
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/member.definition: Indicates a member of a Group

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/membershipClas.label: membershipClass
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/membershipClas.definition: Indicates the class of individuals that are a member of a Group

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/topic.label: topic
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/topic.definition: A topic of some page or document.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/pastProject.label: past project
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/pastProject.definition: A project this person has previously worked on.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/phone.label: phone
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/phone.definition: A phone,  specified using fully qualified tel: URI scheme (refs: http://www.w3.org/Addressing/schemes.html#tel).

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/plan.label: plan
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/plan.definition: A .plan comment, in the tradition of finger and '.plan' files.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/publications.label: publications
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/publications.definition: A link to the publications of this person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/schoolHomepage.label: schoolHomepage
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/schoolHomepage.definition: A homepage of a school attended by the person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/status.label: status
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/status.definition: A string expressing what the user is happy for the general public (normally) to know about their current activity.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/tipjar.label: tipjar
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/tipjar.definition: A tipjar document for this agent, describing means for payment and reward.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/topic_interest.label: topic_interest
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/topic_interest.definition: A thing of interest to this person.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/weblog.label: weblog
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/weblog.definition: A weblog of some thing (whether person, group, company etc.).

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/workInfoHomepa.label: work info homepage
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/workInfoHomepa.definition: A work info homepage of some person; a page about their work for some organization.

http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/workplaceHomep.label: workplace homepage
http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/workplaceHomep.definition: A workplace homepage of some person; the homepage of an organization they work for.
